data.description: Welcome Home to your beautiful brick ranch home, nessled in the quite Rangeview neighborhood of Westminster. This home boasts 4 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, 2100 square feet, 8125 sq ft lot, open concept main floor, large great room in the basement and plenty more. As you enter you are greeted with lots of natural light, beautiful hardwood flooring and a nice open layout. Your main level offers an oversized primary bedroom, a secondary bedroom, updated full bathroom, nice dining room, kitchen and the great room! Making your way downstairs you will find yourself in a lart great room with plenty of room to entertain, across the hall you have an oversized utility / laundry room with a lot of storage space. Down the hall you will find another two bedrooms and an updated 3/4 bathroom. Outback you have a large covered patio, flat yard with plenty of room to play and a large shed with power! Newer windows, furnace, water heater, and roof replaced in 2016. Close to a swim and fitness center, multiple parks, library, shopping and restaurants. Minutes from lightrail station, I-76/70, I-36 and I-25 so getting anywhere you need to go is easy. Ready for your personal touches to truly make this the home you have been waiting for.
